definitions.definition: The act of expunging , of wiping out; expungement .
Withdrawal in order to make oneself inconspicuous ; the making of oneself inconspicuous.
A shortening , or thinning , of the cervix before or during early labour .

main_definition: The act of expunging , of wiping out; expungement .
secondary_definitions: Withdrawal in order to make oneself inconspicuous ; the making of oneself inconspicuous.
( medicine ) A shortening , or thinning , of the cervix before or during early labour .
